column16: Cheslor Cuthbert grounds out, pitcher Adalberto Mejia to first baseman Trevor Plouffe.
Paulo Orlando flies out to center fielder Eddie Rosario.
Christian Colon doubles (5) on a pop up to shortstop Jorge Polanco.   Alex Gordon scores.
Alcides Escobar lines out to right fielder Danny Santana.
Alex Gordon hits a ground-rule double (12) on a line drive to right field.
Salvador Perez pops out to shortstop Jorge Polanco.
Kendrys Morales walks.   Cheslor Cuthbert to 3rd.    Eric Hosmer to 2nd.
Eric Hosmer singles on a line drive to left fielder Robbie Grossman.   Cheslor Cuthbert to 2nd.
Lorenzo Cain out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Eddie Rosario.   Paulo Orlando scores.
Cheslor Cuthbert singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Eddie Rosario, deflected by pitcher Adalberto Mejia.   Paulo Orlando to 3rd.
Paulo Orlando singles on a ground ball to right fielder Danny Santana.
Twins challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was overturned: Christian Colon grounds out sharply, pitcher Adalberto Mejia to first baseman Trevor Plouffe.
Alcides Escobar grounds out, third baseman Eduardo Escobar to first baseman Trevor Plouffe.
